# report-generation-system

Core Report Generation Components:

1. Daily Progress Notes (DPN) Generator
Importance Score: 95
- AI-enhanced narrative generation from behavioral data points (must be reviewed and signed off by qualified clinical staff prior to inclusion in official records)
- Multi-domain analysis across peer/adult interactions, investment, authority
- Real-time performance rating integration 
- Custom clinical terminology mapping
- Automated intervention recommendations based on behavioral patterns (requires clinician validation of any suggested interventions)
- Human oversight, accountability, and versioned audit/log entries documenting reviewer identity and decision rationale are mandated for compliance with clinical and legal standards

2. Clinical Service Plan Reports
Importance Score: 90
- 60-day compliance cycle tracking
- Treatment objective monitoring with progress indicators
- Multi-source data aggregation (behavior, academics, incidents)
- AI-assisted clinical narrative synthesis
- Professional documentation standards enforcement

3. Progress Evaluation Reports
Importance Score: 85
- Weekly/monthly progress calculations
- Domain-specific rating aggregation
- Behavioral trend analysis with AI insights
- Pass schedule integration
- Treatment milestone tracking

4. Court Report Generation
Importance Score: 85
- Legal documentation standards compliance
- Treatment progress summarization
- Incident history compilation
- Behavioral improvement metrics
- Placement recommendation logic (AI-suggested only: must undergo human professional review and advisory until legally reviewed and signed off)
- Professional/legal review required
- Human accountability for final placement recommendations
- Attorney or legal staff involvement required for sign-off before submission to finalize court documentation

Key Business Logic Patterns:
- Clinical terminology standardization
- Treatment progress metrics calculation
- AI-enhanced narrative generation
- Professional documentation compliance
- Multi-domain behavioral analysis

The system implements specialized logic for youth treatment documentation with emphasis on clinical standards, behavioral analysis, and AI-assisted narrative generation.

